{"tid":1653224,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我係頭先求片嘅巴打","createTime":"2019-10-14T03:50:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T05:00:13.000Z","uid":231478,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c770428a0d82849554c36e4eec0d612a456b6b3d","tid":1653224,"uid":231478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T03:50:33.000Z","msg":"好對唔住 我其實係想比中立老母睇成件事嘅經過<br />\n唔想佢比偽中立真藍絲嘅師奶 搞到佢變藍絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今朝新聞報導（ok嗰單） 講到班手足打普通市民咁 睇到我好撚嬲 想幫手足平反<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後就係度開post on99咁就要片<br />\n完全無進一步考慮過班手足嘅安全<br />\n真係好對唔住<br />\n係我on9係我蠢 你地可以屌我on9屌我蠢屌我唔為班手足諗<br />\n但唔好屌我係狗 係mon post狗 因為我唔想舊垃圾代替我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（我個人就去過10幾次遊行 我知相對翻前線嘅付出 我依d唔算d咩 但我都只係想澄清翻自己唔係狗）<br />\n<br />\n最後最後 mon post狗死全家<br />\n黑警死全家<br />\n今晚見！<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">真係好對唔住大家</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n求大家睇完就算 善用不推文回覆 推其他行動po重要過依嗰po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4919d3a325f69c3d372c34c8f207352655aa1dab","tid":1653224,"uid":231478,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T03:51:33.000Z","msg":"好對唔住大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3d2432667a30240f774213b89254b45fdc7a4b7","tid":1653224,"uid":231478,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T03:52:43.000Z","msg":"唔好屌我係mon post狗啦 好無<img src=\"/